cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper presents a new method for reinforcement learning that uses models of state dynamics and the costate equation to improve the policy. Therefore, it is likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with time-optimal control problems and mechanical systems, indicating that it could also be classified under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper uses a model to learn from mental practice, which suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
